    The Classpect Connector — sitemap

    Only REAL HTML pages live here. The site's classpect/class/aspect
    routes (e.g. /#/classpect/witch-of-light) are hash fragments, and
    Google strips fragments before deduplication, so listing them
    would have made every classpect URL look like a duplicate of the
    root page — which is what tanked indexing through April 2026.
    The 144 classpect detail pages are intentionally omitted; revisit
    once they're served at real pathnames (static-generation pass or
    a 404.html SPA rewrite).
